quran[357]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Soni nganitutulusya pa ŵandu ŵakwe panyuma pa jwalakwejo asilikali kuumila kwinani (ŵakwisa kwajonanga), soni nganikuŵa kwakusosekwa Kukwetu kuti mpaka tutulusye (asilikali)"
  36,29,"Nganikuŵa (konanjidwa kwao) ikaŵeje ni n’gumiilo umpepe (uŵagumisile Jibulilu), basi papopo ŵaliji ŵakulita (ŵawile)"
  36,30,"Ha! Yakudandaulisya kwa achikapolo (ŵa Allah)! Nganiŵaichilileje ntenga jwalijose, ikaŵeje ŵaliji nkuntenda chipongwe"
  36,31,Ana ngakulola (yanti) mikutula jilingwa jatujijonasile paujo pao? (Ana ngakulola) yanti ŵanganyao ngaakuujila kukwao
  36,32,Soni pangali (iwumbe) iliyose ikaŵeje yosope yene ichiyika pameso Petu
  36,33,"Soni chilosyo (chachili) kwa ŵanganyao (chakulosya ukombosi wa Allah wakwajimusya ŵawe) ni litaka lyaliwe, tukasalisyusyaga, ni koposyamo songolo, basi sine mu syalakwesyo akasalyaga"
  36,34,"Ni tukasaŵikaga mwalakwemo migunda ja mitende ni mizabibu, ni tukasapitisyaga soni mwalakwemo achitutumule"
  36,35,"Kuti alyeje isogosi yakwe, kutendaga nganiyipanganyidwa ni makono gao, ana ngakutogolela"
  36,36,"Kuswejela ni Kwakwe Ajula (Allah) jwagumbile chachilume ni chachikongwe mu indu yosope, kutandila yaikumesya litaka, ni mwa achimisyene ŵakweo (ŵandu), ni mu ichindu yangakuimanyilila"
  36,37,"Soni chilosyo (chine chachili) kwa ŵanganyao (chakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) ni chilo, tukasawuwulaga mwalakwemo muusi, basi papopo ŵanganyao ni akasaŵaga m’chipi"
  36,38,"Sano lyuŵa likasajendaga mpaka pakutulalila pakwe. Walakweo ni mpango wa (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  36,39,"Nombe nao mwesi twaupimile mauto (makumi gaŵili kwisa nsano nagatatu), mpaka ukasaujaga kuŵa mpela chikole cha tende chakalakala (chepindiche)"
  36,40,"Nganiyiŵa yakuŵajilwa lyuŵa kuwuyika mwesi, namuno chilo kuwulongolela muusi. Soni chilichose ching’ambila mwitala lyasyungulilo"
  36,41,"Soni chilosyo (chine chachili) kwa ŵanganyao (chakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) ni chanti: Uwwe twajigele achatati ŵao m’chombo chepachile (cha ndaŵi ja Nuhu)"
  36,42,Ni twaguumbiile ŵanganyao (yombo) yakulandana mpela chalakwecho yaakukwela
  36,43,"Sano Uwwe naga tuli tusachile mpaka twamisye, ni pangali nkwakamuchisya ŵanganyao (jwampaka apikane gumila kwao), soni ŵanganyao ngaŵa nkokoledwa"
  36,44,"Ikaŵeje kwa chanasa chakuuma Kukwetu, ni kusengwa kwa ndema jannono"
  36,45,"Sano pati iŵechetedwe kukwao yanti: “Jogopani yaili paujo penu ni yaili panyuma penu kuti ntendeledwe chanasa;” (ngakasapikana)"
  36,46,"Ni changaichilila chilosyo chilichose mu ilosyo ya M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ikaŵeje ŵanganyao akasaŵaga ŵakuitundumalila yalakweyo"
  36,47,"Soni pati iŵechetedwe kukwao yanti: “Tolani mu yampele Allah.” Aŵala ŵaakufuulu akasatiji pakwasalila (mwachipongwe) aŵala ŵaakulupilile: “Ana twalisye aŵala ŵanti Allah angasache angalisyisye (Nsyene)? Nganim’ba jenumanja ikaŵeje mu kusokonechela kwakuonechela.”"
  36,48,"Ŵanganyao ni akasatiji: “Ana chele chilanga (chakwika Kiyamachi) chiyiche chakachi nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona?”"
  36,49,Ngakwembecheya ikaŵeje n’gumilo umpepe (lipenga lyandanda) wauchakwembekanya (mwachisupuchisya) aku ali nkukangana
  36,50,"Basi ngasakombola kuleka wasiya, namuno kumaŵasa kwao ngasaujila"
  36,51,"Ni lichigombedwa lipenga (lyaŵili), basi papopo ŵanganyao kuumila m’malembe tachikopokangana mwachitemachitema wa kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah)"
  36,52,"(Aku) achitiji: “Ipotesi yetuwe! Ana ŵani ŵaatujimwisye pagona petu?” (Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Ayi ni ayila yajwapeleche chilanga (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji ni kuŵecheta mwakuona Achimitenga.”"
  36,53,"Ngasiyiŵa ikaŵeje n’gumilo umpepe, basi ajile sayi wosopeŵene tachisimanikwa kuti ayiche pameso Petu"
  36,54,"(Ni tachisalilidwa yanti): “Basi lelo (lisiku lya Kiyama) ngatendedwa lupuso mundu jwalijose pa chilichose, soni ngan’dipidwa ikaŵeje yamwaliji nkupanganya.”"
  36,55,Chisimu ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo lelo taŵe mu shuguli (syao) achisengwaga
  36,56,"Ŵanganyao ni achiŵammakwao taŵe m’miwulili, ali ajegeme mu indanda yetandiche chenene"
  36,57,"Akwete kupata ŵanganyao mwalakwemo isogosi (yantundu uliose), soni akwete kupata chilichose chaakuchisaka"
  36,58,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Salâm (Ntendele uŵe kwa jaomanja!)” – Liloŵe lyakuumila kwa (Allah) M’mbuje Jwachanasa channope"
  36,59,"Sano (ŵangalumbana ni tachisalilidwa kuti): “Litukusyani lelo jenumanja akuleŵa (ku ŵakulupilila)!”"
  36,60,"“Ana nganinan’jamuka, E Jenumanja ŵanache ŵa Adam! Yanti ngasimun’galagatilaga shetani, chisimu jwalakwejo kukwenu juŵele mmagongo jwakuonechela?”"
  36,61,"“Ni kuti mungalagatileje Une (Jikape), lyalakweli ni litala lyagoloka?”"
  36,62,"“Soni chisimu pamasile pajwaisochelesye mu jenumanja iwumbe yejinji, ana nganim’baga ŵakola lunda?”"
  36,63,“Aji ni Jahannama ajila jamwaliji nkupedwa chilanga.”
  36,64,"“Jijinjilani lelo, ligongo lya ukafili wamwaliji nkutenda.”"
  36,65,"Lelo chitusiŵe ngamwa syao, ni gatuŵechetekasye makono gao, ni kuŵichila umboni ngongolo syao pa ayila yaŵaliji nkupanganya"
  36,66,"Sano tungasache chisimu tungafufwite meso gao, mwanti angalimbanilene litala, nambo angalolite chantiuli"
  36,67,"Soni tungasache tungasyusisye (kuŵa inyama kapena maganga) pamalo pao pepo, ni nganganakombola kuja m’bujo namuno kuwujila munyuma"
  36,68,"Soni jwatukumpaga umi (welewu) tukum’buchisyaga munyuma mukagumbidwe (kakwe, ni jukasaŵa nti chisawu mwanache). Ana ngakuitagaga mulunda (yalakweyi)"
  36,69,"Soni nganitun’jiganya jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) kwimba ilaanga, nambo soni ngaikuŵajilwa kukwakwe (kuŵa nkutunga ilaanga). Nganiyiŵatu ayi (yayiche nayo Muhammadi ﷺ) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo kwisa soni Qur’an jakusalichisya (chilichose)"
  36,70,"Kuti antetele jwali chijumi (jwakulupila), ni lisimichiche liloŵe (lya ilagasyo) pa achimakafili"
  36,71,"Ana ngakuiona ŵanganyao yanti Uwwe twaguumbiile ilaango, mu ayila yaipanganyisye makono Getu, basi ŵanganyao ni akuŵa ali nkuitenda kuŵa yao"
  36,72,"Ni twajepepachisye yalakweyo ŵanganyao, basi ine mu yalakweyo iŵele yakwela yao, soni ine mu yalakweyo akasailyaga"
  36,73,"Soni akwete ŵanganyao mwalakwemo yakamuchisya (ine yejinji), kwisa soni yakumwa (mpela nkaka). Ana ngakutogolela"
  36,74,Ni alitendele ŵanganyao milungu (jaunami) kunneka Allah kuti mwine ŵanganyao takamuchisyidwe (ni jalakwejo)
  36,75,"(Nambo) nganijiŵa jikombwele (milungujo) kwakamuchisya ŵanganyao, soni jalakwejo jichisonganganyisyidwa ku ŵanganyao (ndema jakwaŵalanga itendo yao) kuŵa asilikali (ŵakwachonjela)"
  36,76,Basi ikan’dandaulikasya mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) yakuŵecheta yao. Chisimu Uwwe tukuimanya yaakusisa ni yaakulosya
  36,77,"Ana mundu ngajukuiona yanti Uwwe tun’gumbile kuumila mwindondwa lya mesi (ga ŵalume ni ŵakongwe), yeti kaneko jwalakwe ni jukuŵaga mmakaani jwakuonechela (jwakunkanila Allah)"
  36,78,"Ni akutupa Uwwe chilandanyo, ni kuliŵalila kagumbidwe kakwe (kakuumila m’mesi gangali mate). Akutiji: “Ŵani ŵatachigapa umi maupa kutendaga gali gepukuswepukuswe?”"
  36,79,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Tachigapa umi Ajula juŵagagumbile kandanda, soni Jwalakwe chiumbe chilichose juŵele Jwakuchimanya chenene.”"
  36,80,"Ajula jwam’biichiile jenumanja moto m’chitela cheŵisi, basi jenumanja ni nkasakolesyaga (motowo) kuumila muchalakwecho"
  36,81,"Ana nganaŵa Ajula (Allah) juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka jwakombola kuti ŵagumbe (soni ŵandu) ŵanti mpela ŵanganyao? Elo (juŵele Jwakombola kusyene), soni Jwalakwe ni Nkugumba kusyene, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  36,82,"Chisimu chilamusi Chakwe pati asachile chindu (kuti chipatikane), agambaga kuchisalila kuti: “M’be.” Basi ni chikasaŵaga"
  36,83,"Basi kuswejela ni Kwakwe Ajula jwamuli mu Nkono Mwakwe mwana uchimwene wakuchilamulila chindu chilichose, soni Kukwakwe tinchiuchisyidwa (wosope ŵene)"
  37,1,Ngwalumbila aŵala (Achimalaika) ŵaakwima m’miselamisela (pakuswali)
  37,2,Kwisa soni aŵala (Achimalaika) ŵaakasakalipilaga mwamachili (kugakalipila mawunde gawula pakugajendesya)
  37,3,Kwisa soni aŵala (Achimalaika) ŵaakusoomaga chikumbusyo (chitabu pakwikanacho kwa Achimitume kuumila kwa Allah)
  37,4,Chisimu Nnungu jwenu ni Jumpepe
  37,5,"M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, soni M’mbuje jwa kungopoko kosope"
  37,6,Chisimu Uwwe tulisalalisye liwunde lya duniya ni isalalisyo yandondwa
  37,7,Ni kuligosa ku shetani jwalijose jwakunyosya
  37,8,"Kuti akapikanila ya nkutula wa kwinani (wa Achimalaika), ni akasasomedwaga (ni yenje yandondwa) kuumila upande wa mbali ni mbali"
  37,9,"Kuŵinjidwa mwamachili, soni akwete kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope ni kwendelechela"
  37,10,"Ikaŵeje jwasombwele liloŵe mwawiyi, basi ni kunkuya chenje chakuŵala nnope"
  37,11,"Basi mwawusyani (achimakafilio kuti): “Ana ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakusausya nnope kagumbidwe, kapena ayila (ine mpela mawunde, mataka ni matumbi) yatwaigumbile?” Chisimu Uwwe twagumbile jamanjao kuumila mwilongo lyakunyata"
  37,12,"(Ngwamba), nambo mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkusimonga (kanila kwao yakwimuka m’malembe), sano ŵanganyao ni akutenda chipongwe (kuntenda mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ ni Qur’an)"
  37,13,Soni naga ali akumbusyidwe ŵangakumbuchila
  37,14,Soni naga ali achiweni chisimosimo akasachitenda chipongwe
  37,15,"Ni akasatiji: “Nganichiŵatu achi ikaŵeje usaŵi wakuonechela.”"
  37,16,"“Ana patuchiwapo ni kusyuka uwwejo litaka ni maupa, nambo yakuona kuti uwwe tuchiukulidwa (m’malembe)?”"
  37,17,“Mpaka ni achatati ŵetu ŵandanda (nombenao tachiukulidwa)?”
  37,18,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Elo (tinchiukulidwa), soni jenumanja n’di ŵakunyosyeka.”"
  37,19,"Basi chisimu kwalakwe (kuukulidwako) kuchiŵa ni n’gumilo umpepe (walipenga lyaŵili), basi papopo ŵanganyao tachiŵa ali nkulola"
  37,20,"Ni tachiti: “Ipotesi yetuwe! Ali ni Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”"
  37,21,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Ali ni Lisiku Lyachiilanyo alila lyamwaliji jenumanja n’di nkulikanila.”"
  37,22,"(Achimalaika tachisalilidwa yanti): “Mwasonganganyani aŵala ŵaŵalitesile lupuso, pamo ni achimijao (ŵachijini), kwisa soni (isanamu) ayila yaŵaliji nkuigalagatila.”"
  37,23,“Kunneka Allah; basi mwajongolelani kwitala lya ku Moto Waukali.”
  37,24,"“Soni mwajimikani, chisimu ŵanganyao ali ŵakuwusyidwa.”"
  37,25,"“Chipali chichi kukwenu, uli ngankukamusyangana?”"
  37,26,"(Ngwamba), nambo ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo tachiŵa ŵakulipeleka (kuchilamusi cha Allah)"
  37,27,Ni tachigalauchilana ŵane kwa ŵane achiwusyanaga
  37,28,"(Ŵangalikombolela) tachiti (pakwadandaula achinkulungwa ŵao): “Chisimu ŵanganyammwe mwaliji nkutuyichilila chakun’dyo (mukayiche kanti mpela kambone, kwekula kwaliji kutuloŵesya)!”"
  37,29,"(Achinkulungwa) tachiti: “(Ngwamba), nambo jenumanja nganim’ba ŵakulupilila.”"
  37,30,"“Soni uwwe nganitukola machili galigose pa jenumanja (gakunkanganichisya ukafili), nambo kuti jenumanja mwaliji ŵandu ŵakusumba mpika (pa ukafili mpela uwwewe).”"
  37,31,"“Basi liloŵe lya Ambuje ŵetu (Allah lyakupedwa ilagasyo) lisimichiche petuwe, chisimu uwwe chitupasye (ilagasyoyo).”"
  37,32,“Basi twansochelesye (ligongo lyanti nombe) uwwe chisimu chene twaliji ŵasochelele.”
  37,33,Basi chisimu ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo tachiŵa yalumo mu ilagasyo
  37,34,Chisimu Uwwe mwele ni mutukwatendelaga ŵakuleŵa
  37,35,"Chisimu ŵanganyao ndema jakuŵechetedwa kukwao yanti: Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Allah; ŵaliji nkulikwesya"
  37,36,"Ni kuŵechetaga yanti: “Ana chisimu uwwe tuleche milungu jetu ligongo lya nkwimba ilaanga, jwamasoka?”"
  37,37,"(Ngwamba), nambo juyiche ni yakuona, soni jwajitichisye Achimitenga (ŵaŵalongolele)"
  37,38,"Chisimu ŵanganyammwe (achimakafili ŵa pa Maaka), timpasye ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"
  37,39,Soni ngallipidwa ikaŵeje yamwaliji nkupanganya
  37,40,Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa
  37,41,Ŵanganyao akwete kupata lisiki lyakumanyika
  37,42,"Isogosi (yantundu uliose), soni ŵanyao takachimbichisyidwe"
  37,43,Ku Matimbe Gachindimba (ku Mbepo)
  37,44,Ali (atemi) pa itengu yauchimbichimbi mwakulolegana
  37,45,Tiikaŵeje ili nkwasyungula ipanda ya ukana ŵakulenjela
  37,46,Weswela wakulyolyopela kwa akumwa
  37,47,"Mwangali mwele (mu ukanamo) yakupotekasya (ntwe namuno m’matumbo), nambo soni ŵanganyao ngasakolelwa nao"
  37,48,"Soni kukwao tikukaŵe kwana (achiŵammakwao) ŵakulola pejipi (ŵakwalola achalume ŵaope ŵangatenda meso mwamwamwa kwa achalume ŵane), achakulungwa meso mwakusalalila"
  37,49,Gamba kuŵa (kaswejele kao) ŵanganyao nti chisawu mandanda gagasunjidwe (m’mapapiko)
  37,50,Basi tachigalauchilana ŵane kwa ŵane achiwusyanaga
  37,51,"Nkuŵecheta jumpepe mwa ŵanganyao tachiti: “Chisimu une nakwete n’jangu (kuduniya).”"
  37,52,"“Juŵaliji nkuti: ‘Ana mmwe chisimu chene n’di mwa akwitichisya?’"
  37,53,"‘(Yanti) patuchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupa, nambo yakuona uwwe tuchilipidwa (pa itendo yetu)?”"
  37,54,"(Nkuŵecheta jula) tachiti: “Ana jenumanja chin’dingule (none ku Moto kuti mum’bone yajukuti pakulagasika?” Ŵanganyao tachiti: “Iyayi.”)"
  37,55,"Basi jwalakwe ni juchilingula, basi ni tachim’bona (n’jakwejula) juli nkatikati mwa Moto Waukali"
  37,56,"Juchiti: “Ngunnumbila Allah! Mmwetu mwasigele panandi kuti munyonanje (ngampikanile).”"
  37,57,"“Soni ungaŵaga ukoto wa Ambuje ŵangu (Allah), ningaliji mwa akwika nao (ku Moto).”"
  37,58,"(Ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo tachiti): “Ana uwweji nikuti ngatuwa (soni)?”"
  37,59,"“Ikaŵeje chiwa chetu chandandapechila, soni uwwe ngatulagasyidwa?”"
  37,60,Chisimu kwalakweku ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope
  37,61,"Pa (kusaka kupata) yanti mpela ayi, basi apanganye masengo (gambone) akupanganya"
  37,62,"Ana yalakweyi ni mbiko jambone, kapena chitela cha Zakkum"
  37,63,"Chisimu Uwwe tuchitesile chele (chitelacho) kuŵa mayeso ku ŵalupuso (pakuŵecheta ŵanganyao kuti: “Mpaka ikomboleche uli chitela kumela m’moto)?”"
  37,64,Chisimu chalakwecho ni chitela chachikopoka kuumila pasi pasyesyene pa Moto Waukali
  37,65,Soso sya isogosi yakwe (siŵele syakunyalaya nnope) mpela mitwe ja mashetani
  37,66,"Basi chisimu ŵanganyao takalyeje chele (chitelacho), ni chalakwecho takagumbasyeje ndumbo syao"
  37,67,Kaneko chisimu akwete kupata ŵanganyao kupwatika pa chele (chitelacho) chakuwanganyichisya gagali mesi gamasemule nnope
  37,68,Kaneko chisimu kwakuwujila kwao ni ku Moto Waukali
  37,69,Chisimu ŵanganyao ŵasimene achatati ŵao ali ŵapotele
  37,70,Sano ŵanganyao mu sajo syao akutugala (pakwakuya mwachitemachitema mwangali kusosa kaje umboni)
  37,71,Soni chisimu ŵapotele paujo pao ŵajinji (mu ŵandu) ŵandanda
  37,72,Soni chisimu twatumisye mwa ŵanganyao akutetela
  37,73,Basi nnole mujaŵelele mbesi ja akuteteledwa
  37,74,Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa
  37,75,"Soni chisimu Nuhu jwatuŵilasile (kuti tun’jokole), basi ni Akwanga Ŵambone nnope (twaliji Uwwe)"
  37,76,Ni twan’jokwele jwalakwe ni ŵapeŵasa ŵakwe ku taabu jekulungwa
  37,77,Ni twatesile ŵanache ŵakwe kuŵa sigasiga (ŵaŵasigele ali nkuŵelekana paduniya)
  37,78,Ni twannechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma
  37,79,Ntendele uŵe kwa Nuhu mu iwumbe yosope
  37,80,Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  37,81,Chisimu jwalakwe (Nuhu) jwaliji mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵakulupilila
  37,82,Kaneko ni twamisyisye ŵane (wosope mwa ŵangakulupilila)
  37,83,Soni chisimu mwa aŵala ŵaŵakuyiye litala lyakwe (lya Nuhu lya Tauhidi) jwaliji Ibrahima
  37,84,Ndema ja ŵaichilile Ambujegwe (Allah) ni ntima wambonembonepe
  37,85,"Ndema ja jwatite kwa babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe: “Ana nkugalagatila chichi?”"
  37,86,“Ana mwaunaminamipe milungu jangaŵaga Allah ni jankujisaka?”
  37,87,“Ana nganisyo syenu sili uli pa ya M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope?”
  37,88,Kaneka ni jwalolite kulola (kwakuchetelela) ku ndondwa
  37,89,"Ni jwatite: “Chisimu une jwakulwala.”"
  37,90,Basi ŵanganyao ŵantundumalile jwalakwe mwakunnochesya migongo
  37,91,"Basi jwalakwe ni jwapite mwagwala ku milungu jao, ni jwatite: “Uli ngankulya (yakulya yam’bichileyi)?”"
  37,92,"“Chipali chichi kukwenu, uli ngankuŵecheta?”"
  37,93,Kaneka ni jwajigalauchile pakujiputa ni nkono wakwe wan’dyo (kwamachili gakwe gosope)
  37,94,Basi (paŵapikene achinsyene isanamuyo) ŵam’bichilile ali nkutugala
  37,95,"(Jwalakwe) jwatite: “Ana nkuigalagatila yankuisepa (mwachimisyene)?”"
  37,96,“Kutendaga Allah ni juŵan’gumbile jemanjammwe ni yankupanganya!”
  37,97,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Muntaŵilani chakutaŵa (chiwukuta) ni mumponye m’moto waukali.”"
  37,98,"Basi ŵasachile kuntendela jwalakwe malindi, ni twatesile kuŵa ŵapasi kusyene"
  37,99,"(Ibrahima) ni jwatite: “Chisimu une ngwaula kwa Ambuje ŵangu (Allah), takanjongole.”"
  37,100,“Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbani (mwanache jwa) mu ŵandu ŵambone.”
  37,101,Basi ni twansengwasyisye ni abali ja (kola) mwanache jwakulitimalika (jwali Ismaila)
  37,102,"Basi ndema jajwayiche (mwanachejo) pa nsingu wakwenda najo imo, (Ibrahima) jwatite: “E mwanangu! Chisimu une naiweni kulugono yanti une ngunsikita mmwe (kuŵa mbepesi jakupeleka kwa Allah), basi nnole (nganisyo syenu), nkuiona uli?” (Mwanache) jwatite: “E baba ŵangu! Tendani yannamulidwe, timusimane une nasakaga Allah ndili mwa akupilila.”"
  37,103,"Basi ndema jaŵalipeleche ŵanaŵaŵili (ku chilamusi cha Allah), (Ibrahima) ni ŵan’goneche chamakuku (Ismaila kuti ansikite)"
  37,104,"Uwwe ni twam’bilasile kuti: “E mmwe Ibrahima!”"
  37,105,“Chisimu pamasile pankwanilisye sagamisi.” Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukasatiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  37,106,Chisimu galakwega ni mayeso gakuonechela
  37,107,Ni twam’bombwele (nkusikitidwajo) ni chakusikitidwa chekulungwa (ngondolo)
  37,108,Ni twannechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma
  37,109,Ntendele uŵe kwa Ibrahima
  37,110,Iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  37,111,Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵakulupilila
  37,112,"Ni twansengwasyisye ni abali ja (kum’beleka) Isihaka, Ntume jwa mu ŵandu ŵambone"
  37,113,Ni twampele upile jwalakwe ni Isihaka jwakwe. Sano mu ŵanache ŵao mwana nkukolosya (itendo yakwe) ni nkulitenda lupuso nsyene mwakuonechela
  37,114,Soni chisimu chene twampele ukoto Musa ni Haruna
  37,115,Ni twajokwele ŵanaŵaŵilio ni ŵandu ŵao ku taabu jekulungwa
  37,116,"Ni twakamuchisye, basi ni ŵaliji ŵanganyao ŵakupunda"
  37,117,Ni twapele ŵanaŵaŵilio chitabu chakusalichisya
  37,118,Ni twajongolele kwitala lyagoloka
  37,119,Ni twalechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma
  37,120,Ntendele uŵe kwa Musa ni Haruna
  37,121,Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  37,122,Chisimu ŵanaŵaŵilio ŵaliji mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵakulupilila
  37,123,Soni chisimu Iliyasa jwaliji mwa Achimitenga
  37,124,"(Kumbuchilani) ndema jajwatite ku ŵandu ŵakwe: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  37,125,"“Ana nkum’bomba Ba’la ni kunneka jwali Jwambone nnope mwa akugumba,”"
  37,126,"“Allah, M’mbuje gwenu nambo soni M’mbuje jwa achatati ŵenu ŵandanda?”"
  37,127,"Basi ŵankaaniile, basi chisimu ŵanganyao tachiika nao (ku ilagasyo)"
  37,128,Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa
  37,129,Ni twannechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma
  37,130,Ntendele uŵe kwa Ilyaasiin
  37,131,Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  37,132,Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵakulupilila
  37,133,Soni chisimu Lutwi jwaliji mwa Achimitenga
  37,134,(Kumbuchilani) ndema jatwan’jokwele jwalakwe ni liŵasa lyakwe lyosopelyene
  37,135,Ikaŵeje kangalamba kachikongwe (ŵankwao Lutwi ŵaŵaliji) mwa akusigalila munyuma
  37,136,Kaneko ni twajonasile ŵaneo
  37,137,Soni chisimu ŵanganyammwe nkwapitaga ŵanganyao (misi jao) kundaŵi
  37,138,"Ni chilo chakwe, ana ŵangali lunda"
  37,139,Soni chisimu Yunusu jwaliji mwa Achimitenga
  37,140,(Kumbuchilani) ndema ja jwatilile m’chombo chepachile
  37,141,"Basi ni ŵatesile ndoto (kuti ŵatijagwile ndotojo aponyedwe m’mesi), basi ni jwaliji (Yunusu) mwa akwagwila (ndoto)"
  37,142,Basi ni chammisile chinsomba aku juli jwagambidwa
  37,143,Basi ingaŵa kuti jwalakwe jwaliji mwa akunswejesya (Allah)
  37,144,Chisimu jungatemi m’matumbo mwakwe kwikanila lisiku lyakuwukulidwa (ŵandu m’malembe)
  37,145,Basi twamponyisye munjengwe jambembembe juli jwakulwala
  37,146,Ni twammechesye chitela cha mongumbondu (mbonda syekulungwa syati mpela mongu)
  37,147,"Ni twantumisye ku (ŵandu) masausande gakwana lichila (,000) nambo soni ŵakupunda pele"
  37,148,"Ni ŵakulupilile, basi ni twasengwasyisye kwikanila ndema (jao jakuwila)"
  37,149,"Basi mwawusyani (achimakafili ŵa pa Maaka mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ kuti): “Ana Ambuje ŵenu ni akwete ŵanache ŵachikongwe, sano ŵanganyao ni akwete ŵanache ŵachilume?”"
  37,150,“Kapena twagumbile Achimalaika kuŵa achakongwe aku ŵanganyao achitendelaga umboni?”
  37,151,"Manyililani yanti, ŵanganyao ni unami ŵao akuŵechetaga yanti"
  37,152,“Allah aŵeleche (ŵanache ŵachikongwe ŵali Achimalaika).” Soni chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami kusyene
  37,153,Ana (Allah) jusagwile ŵanache ŵachikongwe kwaleka ŵachilume
  37,154,"Chipali chichi kukwenu, ana nkulamula chinauli"
  37,155,Ana ngankukumbuchila (yanti Allah juŵambalene nayo yakola mwanache)
  37,156,Kapena jenumanja nkwete umboni wakuonechela (wa yankuŵechetayi)
  37,157,Basi ikani nacho chitabu chenu nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona
  37,158,Ni asepelele ŵanganyao ulongo chilikati cha Jwalakwe (Allah) ni majini. Nambo majini ni gamanyiliile kusyene yanti chisimu ŵanganyao (achimakafilio) tachija kuonechela (kwa Allah kuti akajiilanye magambo ga unami wao)
  37,159,Allah aŵambalene nayo kusyene yaakusimba ŵanganyao
  37,160,Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa (ŵanganyao ni ŵaakunswejesya Allah ku yaakunnambuchisya achimakafili)
  37,161,Sano chisimu jenumanja (achimakafili) ni yankuigalagatila (isanamu)
  37,162,Nganim’ba jenumanja ŵanti ni kunsochelesyanayo (jwalijose mu ŵakulupilila kuti anneche Allah)
  37,163,Ikaŵeje ajula jwatakajinjile ku Moto Waukali
  37,164,Soni pangali jwalijose mwetuwe (Achimalaika) ikaŵeje jukwete malo gakumanyika (kwinani gakutendela ibada)
  37,165,Soni chisimu uwwe (Achimalaika) tukwimaga m’misela (pakuswali)
  37,166,Soni chisimu uwwe (Achimalaika) tukunswejesyaga (Allah pa kuswali)
  37,167,Soni chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (achimakafili ŵacharabu) ŵatiji
  37,168,"“Ingaŵe twakwete uwwe chikumbusyo muŵakolele ŵandu ŵandanda,”"
  37,169,“Chisimu tungaliji achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa.”
  37,170,"Basi (pachaichilile chikumbusyo) ŵachikanile, basi tachiyika kumanyilila (yatinjatenda)"
  37,171,Soni chisimu chene pamasile pa lyalongolele liloŵe Lyetu kwa achikapolo Ŵetu Achimitenga
  37,172,(Lyanti) chisimu ŵanganyao ni ŵatakamuchisyidwe
  37,173,Nambo soni kuti asilikali Ŵetu chisimu ni ŵataŵe ŵakupunda
  37,174,Basi mwatundumalilani kwa kandaŵi kannono
  37,175,Soni gambagani kwalola; basi sampano taione
  37,176,Ana akuijanguya ilagasyo Yetu
  37,177,"Basi (ilagasyo) patiichituluchila paluŵala pao (tachijonanjidwa), ni kuchiŵa kundaŵi kwakusakala nnope kwa akuteteledwa"
  37,178,Soni mwatundumalilani kwa kandaŵi kannono
  37,179,Soni gambagani kwalola; basi sampano taione
  37,180,"Aŵambalene kusyene Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), Ambuje ŵamachili gakupunda ku yaakwasimba nayo (achimakafili)"
  37,181,Soni ntendele uŵe kwa Achimitenga
  37,182,Soni lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  38,1,"Swâd, ngujilumbila Qur’an jajikwete chikumbusyo"
  38,2,Nambo aŵala ŵaakufuulu ali nkulikwesya ni kusisya
  38,3,"Ana mikutula jilingwa jatwajijonasile paujo pao! Ni ŵagumisile, kutendaga ndema jakokochela jili jipitene"
  38,4,"Ni akusimonga ya kwaichilila nkutetela kuumila mwa jamanjao, achimakafili ni akutiji: “Aju ni nsaŵi, jwaunami kusyene.”"
  38,5,“Ana jujitesile milungu (josope) kuŵa nnungu jumo! Chisimu chalakwechi ni chindu chakusimosya.”
  38,6,"Ni ŵaŵigwile achinkulungwa mwa ŵanganyao (kupita nchigombelesya yanti): “Jendelechelani (pa dini jenu), soni jipililililani milungu jenu (pa kujigalagatila), chisimu chalakwechi ni chindu (chakusakala) chachikusachikwa (kukwetu, chakuti tuleche dini jetu).”"
  38,7,"“Nganitupikaneje yalakweyi (yakuŵa nnungu jumo namuno) mu dini jambesiji (ja chikilisito), nganiyiŵatu ayi ikaŵeje unami.”"
  38,8,"“Ana pa chilikati petu chikumbusyo ni chitulusyiidwe kukwakwe (pe)?” Nambo ŵanganyao ali mu kaichila ya chikumbusyo Changu, nambo nganapasye ilagasyo (Yangu)"
  38,9,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao imatiilo ya ukoto ŵa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵakupeleka kwannope"
  38,10,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe? Basi (naga ili iyyo), akwele m’makwelelo (kuja kwinani)"
  38,11,(Aga makafiliga pamo ni kulikwesya kwao) kaŵele kankutula kangali machili mwanti tikakomboledwe yagatite pakomboledwa makuga (ga makafili) kalakala (gagakanilaga utenga wa Achimitume)
  38,12,"Ŵakaaniile paujo pao ŵandu ŵa Nuhu, Adi ni Firiauna nsyene ichili (yakulimbanganyichisya uchimwene wakwe; ŵali asilikali)"
  38,13,"Kwisa soni Samuda, ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ni akutama nyyitekete (ŵandu ŵa Shuaibu). Jalakwejo ni mikutula (ja makafili jatwajijonasile)"
  38,14,"Pangali jwalijose mwa jamanjao ikaŵeje jwakaaniile Achimitenga, basi ni yasimichiche ipotesi Yangu"
  38,15,Ni ngakwembecheya ŵanganyaŵa ikaŵeje n’gumilo umpepe (wa lipenga lya Kiyama) wangali kuusyaausya
  38,16,"Ŵanganyao ni akutiji (mwachipongwe): “Ambuje ŵetu! Tupani mwachitema chipande chetu (cha malipilo ga masengo getu gambone ni gakusakala) nkaniliyiche Lisiku Lyachiŵalanjilo.”"
  38,17,"Pililani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) pa yaakuŵecheta, ni munkumbuchile kapolo Jwetu Daudi nsyene machili (gakwendechesya utume ni uchimwene), chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakuujilaujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)"
  38,18,Chisimu Uwwe twagajepepesye matumbi kuti gaswejesyeje (Lumbili Lwetu) pamo ni jwalakwe (Daudi) kwigulo ni kundaŵi
  38,19,"Nombe nayo ijuni (yaliji nkuswejesya najo) ili isonganganyisyidwe, yosope yene (matumbi ni ijuni) yaliji yakumpikanila (Daudi)"
  38,20,"Ni twaulimbangenye uchimwene wakwe, ni twampele lunda lwakusokoka nambo soni kwilanya chenene magambo (ni chine chilichose)"
  38,21,Ana jinyyiche abali ja akukangana ndema ja ŵakwesile lipupa mpaka kwinjila ku chigunguli (chakuswalila Daudi)
  38,22,"Ndema ja ŵan’jinjilile Daudi, basi jwalakwe ni ŵajogwepe ŵanganyao. Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Nkajogopa, (uwwe ni) akukangana ŵaŵili, jumo jwetu ankotwesye n’jakwe, basi jilanyani chilikati chetu mwachilungamiko ni nkajimila mbali, soni tujongolelani kwitala lyagoloka.”"
  38,23,"“Chisimu aju nnongo n’jangu; jukwete ngondolo syekongwe makumi nsano nancheche kwisa nsano nancheche , sano une ni ngwete ngondolo jekongwe jimope, sano ni jukuti: ‘Mumbani jimojo nansunjile.’ (Sano une nansyene ni ngangusaka), ni jumbundile pa kaŵechete.”"
  38,24,"(Daudi) jwatite: “Chisimu antesile lupuso pakuŵenda ngondolo jenu jekongwe kuti ajiwanganye ku ngondolo syakwe syekongwe, chisimu ŵajinji mwa akuwanganya nao ichindu akasakotosyanaga ŵane ni ŵane, ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, soni ŵanti iyyoyowo nganatupa.” Ni jwasimichisye Daudi kuti chisimu tun’dinjile mayeso, basi ni jwaaŵendile chikululuko Ambujegwe (Allah), ni jwasenjelemukwiche kwinama (kuswali) ni jwaujile (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)"
  38,25,"Basi twankululuchile yalakweyo, soni chisimu jwalakwe jukwete Kukwetu uchimbichimbi kwisa soni malo gambone nnope gakuujila (ku Mbepo)"
  38,26,"“E mmwe Daudi! Chisimu Uwwe tuntesile mmwe kuŵa ŵakulolela pachilambo, basi jilanyani chilikati cha ŵandu mwa chilungamiko, soni ngasinkuya isako (yantima wenu) itakwisa mwainsokonesye kuleka litala lya Allah. Chisimu aŵala ŵaakusokonechela kuleka litala lya Allah, akwete kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yaukali nnope ligongo lyakuliŵalila kwao Lisiku Lyachiŵalanjilo.”"
  38,27,Ni nganitugumba mawunde ni mataka ni yaili chilikati chakwe mwamasanje. Syele ni nganisyo sya aŵala ŵaakufuulu. Basi ipotesi yakuumila ku Moto takaipate aŵala ŵaakufuulu
  38,28,Ana twatende aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone nti chisawu akuwatanganya pachilambo? Kapena twatende ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) nti chisawu akuleŵa
  38,29,(Achi ni) Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chatuchitulwisye kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) chaupile wejinji kuti agachetelele (ŵandu) ma Ȃya gakwe ni kuti ŵakwete lunda akumbuchile
  38,30,Ni twampele Daudi (mwanache lina lyakwe) Sulaimana. Kaje umbone nnope kapolo jwakwe! Chisimu jwalakwe (Sulaimana) jwaliji jwakuujilaujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)
  38,31,"(Kumbuchilani) ndema ja syaonesyedwe kukwakwe kwigulo hachi syakutulala nnope pati sijimi, syakuutuka nnope"
  38,32,"Basi jwatite: “Chisimu une nainonyele nnope yambone (hachi), kwakuleka kwakumbuchila Ambuje ŵangu (Allah pangaswali swala ja Asr) mpakana (lyuŵa) lisiŵiliche mu chakusiŵilila (pakutiŵila).”"
  38,33,“Siuchisyani kukwangu (hachisyo).” Basi ni jwatandite kusipukuta sonjo ni ngosi
  38,34,"Soni chisimu twan’dinjile Sulaimana mayeso, ni twaponyisye pa chitengu chakwe (cha uchimwene) chiŵiliŵili (lijini lyalyasumwile uchimwene wakwe kwa kandaŵi), kaneka ni jwaujile (ku uchimwene wakwe)"
  38,35,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mungululuchilani, ni mumbe uchimwene ŵangam’bajila jwalijose panyuma pangune, chisimu Mmwejo ni ŵan’di Ŵakupeleka kwannope.”"
  38,36,Basi twan’jepepachisye mbungo jajajendaga mwambolembole mwa lilalumusi lyakwe (kuja) kulikose kwajukusaka
  38,37,"Ni (twan’jepepachisye soni) mashetani, ŵaliose ŵakutaŵa (yakutaŵataŵa) ni ŵakutiŵila (m’mbwani kukusosa ngalekale)"
  38,38,Sano ŵane ŵaliji ŵagamba kutaŵidwa m’maunyolo (ŵakunyosya malamusi gakwe)
  38,39,"(Allah ŵansalile kuti): “Awu ni ntuka Wetu (watumpele), basi tolani (kumpa jwankunsaka) kapena umbatani, mwangali chiŵalanjilo.”"
  38,40,Soni chisimu jwalakwe jukwete Kukwetu uchimbichimbi kwisa soni malo gambone nnope gakuujila (ku Mbepo)
  38,41,"Soni munkumbuchilani kapolo Jwetu Ayyubu, ndema ja jwaŵilasile Ambujegwe (Allah ni jwatite): “Chisimu une jungwayiye shetani ni masausyo kwisa soni ipotesi.”"
  38,42,"(Allah ŵansalile kuti): “Putisyani lukongolo lwenu (petaka, tipakopoche mesi). Aga (mesi) gakoga gakusisima (basi jogani) nambo soni gakumwa (basi mwaani).”"
  38,43,"Ni twampele ŵapeŵasa ŵakwe ni ŵane ŵanti mpela ŵawowo soni, kuŵa ukoto wakuuma Kukwetu, ni chikumbusyo ku ŵaakwete lunda"
  38,44,"“Soni jigalani munkono mwenu katenje (ka tutela twaŵanaŵana) ni mwapute nako (ŵankwenu pa yangalumbana yaŵatesile), ni nkawesesya kulumbila kwenu.” Chisimu Uwwe twansimene jwalakwe kuti jwaliji jwakupilila. Kaje umbone nnope kapolo jwakwe! Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakuujilaujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)"
  38,45,"Soni mwakumbuchilani achikapolo Ŵetu Ibrahima, Isihaka ni Yaakubu achinsyene machili (gakwendechesya dini) ni kulola (kwaumanyilisi)"
  38,46,Chisimu Uwwe twasagwile ŵanganyao pakwapa ndamo jambone ja kumbuchila Nyumba Jambesi (ja Akhera)
  38,47,Soni chisimu ŵanganyao Kukwetu ŵaliji ŵakusagulidwa soni ŵambone
  38,48,"Soni munkumbuchilani Ismaila, Al-yasa‘a (Eliya) ni Dhul-Kifli (Yesaya), soni ŵosope ŵene ŵaliji mu ŵandu ŵambone"
  38,49,Achi ni chikumbusyo. Sano chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) akwete kupata malo gakuujila gambone nnope
  38,50,"Matimbe Gandamo, gatigakaŵe geugulidwe milango kwaugulila ŵanganyao"
  38,51,"Takaŵe ali ajegeme (mwakwegama) kwalakweko, achiŵilasyaga kwalakweko isogosi yejinji ni yakumwa"
  38,52,"Soni kukwao tikukaŵe kwana (achiŵammakwao) ŵakulola pejipi (ŵakwalola achalume ŵaope ŵangatenda meso mwamwamwa kwa achalume ŵane), ŵakulandana misingu"
  38,53,Ayi ni yankupedwa chilanga ya Lisiku Lyachiŵalanjilo
  38,54,Chisimu ali ni lisiki Lyetu lyangamala
  38,55,Ayi (ichiŵa iyyo). Sano chisimu ŵakusumba mpika (pakunnyosya Allah) akwete kupata malo gakuujila gakusakala nnope
  38,56,"Jahannama, takajijinjile. Basi kaje kusakala liuto lyagusama (lyalitandichile)"
  38,57,Ayi (ichiŵa iyyo). Basi agapasye ŵanganyao galakwe - mesi gamasemule nnope ni uwowu
  38,58,Ni (ipotesi) yine yanti chisawu iyyiyi yamitundumitundu
  38,59,"(Tachisalilidwa akukuyidwa pakuponyedwa kumoto pamo ni akukuya): “Awu ni nkutula waukwinjila pamo ni jenumanja (ku Moto).” (Akukuyidwa tachiti): “Ŵangali pakwichila pambone ŵanganyao. Chisimu ŵanganyao tapye Moto.”"
  38,60,"(Akukuya) tachiti: “Nambo jenumanja ni ŵankuŵajilwa ngakola pakwichila pambone, jenumanja ni ŵantutendekasyisye uwwe kupata ayi (ipotesiyi pakutusochelesya ku duniya), basi kaje kusakala malo gakutamilichika gakwe!”"
  38,61,"Ŵanganyao takajile: “Ambuje ŵetu! Ŵatutendekasyisye uwwe kupata yalakweyi, basi mwajonjechesyani ilagasyo yakaŵili m’Moto.”"
  38,62,"Ŵanganyao ni takajile: “Chipali chichi kukwetu, uli ngatukwaona achalume ŵatwaliji nkwaganichisya kuti ali mu ŵandu ŵakusakala (ligongo lyakunkuya Muhammadi ﷺ)?”"
  38,63,"“Ana twatesile chipongwe (ku duniya kutendaga ali ŵambone ŵakuŵajilwa kwinjila ku Mbepo), kapena gatekwakulusya meso (getu nambo tuli nao imo m’Moto muno)?”"
  38,64,Chisimu ayi ni yakuona yakangana ŵandu ŵa ku Moto
  38,65,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Chisimu une ni nkutetela pe, soni pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Allah Jumpepe, Jwamachili gangalimbana nago.”"
  38,66,"“M’mbuje jwa mawunde ni mataka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakululuka kusyene.”"
  38,67,"Jilani: “Aji (Qur’an) jiŵele abali jekulungwa nnope.”"
  38,68,“Jankujitundumalila ŵanganyammwe.”
  38,69,“Nganingola umanyilisi wakwayana ni nkutula wakwinani (Achimalaika) ndema jawaliji nkukangana (pa yagumbidwa kwa Adam).”
  38,70,"“Nganiyijuwulidwa kukwangu, ikaŵeje yanti une ni nkutetela jwakuonechela.”"
  38,71,"(Kumbuchilani) ndema jaŵaŵechete Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kwa Achimalaika kuti: “Chisimu Une tingumbe mundu kuumila mwilongo.”"
  38,72,"“Sano patimale kunkolosya ni kumpepelela nsimu wakuuma Kukwangu, basi munsenjelemuchile pakunsujudila.”"
  38,73,Basi ni ŵasujudu Achimalaika wosope ŵene nakamo
  38,74,"Ikaŵeje Ibulisu, jwalikwesyisye ni jwaliji mwa makafili"
  38,75,"(Allah) jwatite: “E mmwe Ibulisu! Chichi chinnekasyisye kunsujudila ajula junan’gumbile ni Makono Gangu ganagaŵili? Ana n’dikwesyisye kapena n’di mwa ŵapenani kusyene?”"
  38,76,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Une ni jwambone nnope kumpunda jwalakweju, mwangumbile une kuumila m’moto, ni mun'gumbile jwalakweju kuumila mwilongo"
  38,77,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi kopokani mwalakwemo, mwanti chisimu mmwe (sano) n’di ŵakuŵinjidwa.”"
  38,78,“Soni chisimu pachanya penu pana malweso Gangu mpaka Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  38,79,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbanitu lipesa (lyakuti ngawa) mpaka lisiku lyatachiukulidwa (m’malembe achiiumbe wosope).”"
  38,80,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akupedwa lipesa.”"
  38,81,"“Kwikanila lisiku lya ndema jakumanyika (jagombedwa lipenga lyandanda, pele ni patinchiwila).”"
  38,82,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ngugalumbila machili Genu gakupunda! Tinasokonesye kwene ŵanaose.”"
  38,83,“Pangaŵaga achikapolo Ŵenu ŵakuswejesyedwa mwa ŵanganyao.”
  38,84,"(Allah) jwatite: “Ngulumbila kusyene, soni yakuona nguŵecheta.”"
  38,85,“Tingajigumbasye kwene Jahannama ni mmwe pamo ni ŵataachinkuuya mwa ŵanganyao wosope ŵene.”
  38,86,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo galigose, soni nganimba une mwa akulikanganichisya (kutenda yangaŵa nkuikombola).”"
  38,87,“Nganijiŵatu aji (Qur’an) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo ku iwumbe yosope.”
  38,88,“Soni timmanyilile kwene (kalulila kwa) abali jakwe pangakaŵapa.”
  39,1,"Kutulusyidwa kwa Chitabu (Qur’an) kukuumila kwa Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  39,2,"Chisimu Uwwe tuntuluchisye (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) Chitabu mwakuonaonape, basi mun’galagatilani Allah mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe"
  39,3,"Manyililani yanti Allah akasapochelaga dini jeswela (jangawanganya ni isanamu). Sano aŵala ŵalitendele akwakamuchisya ŵanepe kunneka Jwalakwe (Allah, akasatiji): “Ngatukwagalagatila ŵanganyaŵa ikaŵeje kuti atuŵandichisye kwa Allah nnope.” Chisimu Allah tachijilanya chilikati chao pa ichindu yaŵaliji nkutindana pa yalakweyo. Chisimu Allah ŵangan’jongola mundu jwali jwaunami soni jwakufulu nnope"
  39,4,"Allah angasache kulitendela mwanache angasagwile mu ichindu yaagumbile chaakuchisaka. Kuswejela ni Kwakwe, Jwalakwe ni Allah, Jumpepe, Jwamachili gangalimbana nago"
  39,5,"Jwagumbile mawunde ni mataka mwakuonaonape, akasachiŵiligaga chilo m’muusi ni kuuŵiliga muusi m’chilo, ni alijepepesye lyuŵa ni mwesi, yosope yene ikwenda mpaka pandema jekolanjidwe, manyililani yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakululuka kusyene"
  39,6,"Ŵan’gumbile jenumanja kuumila mwa mundu jumpepe (Adam), ni ŵagumbile kuumila mwa jwalakwejo ŵankwakwe (Hawa), ni antuluchisye ŵanganyammwe kuumila mu ilango mitundu nsano najitatu (ngamiya, ng’ombe, ngondolo ni mbusi chilichose chelume ni chekongwe). Akasan’gumbaga jenumanja mu itumbo ya achimama ŵenu kagumbidwe kane panyuma pa kagumbidwe kane, mu ipi itatu. Jwalakwejotu ni Allah M’mbuje gwenu, Uchimwene ni Wakwe, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwalakwe, basi ana nkugalausyidwa chinauli (kuleka yakuona)"
  39,7,"Naga nkufulu, basi chisimu Allah ngaakunnajila jenumanja, soni ngaakuunonyela ukafili wa achikapolo Ŵakwe. Sano naga nkutogolela taisengwele yalakweyo kukwenu. Soni jwaatwiichiile nsigo (wasambi) ngasaja kutwichila nsigo wajwine, kaneka kwa M'mbuje gwenu (Allah) ni kwakuujila kwenu, basi ni tachintagulila ichindu yamwaliji nkupanganya. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Nkumanyilila yaili m’mitima"
  39,8,"Sano naga mundu chili chinkwayiye chakusausya chilichose akasam’bendaga M’mbujegwe (Allah) mwakuujila Kukwakwe (pakutenda toba). Kaneko nkumpa ukoto wakuuma Kukwakwe, basi jukasaliŵalilaga ayila yajwaliji nkwaŵilanjila ku yalakweyo (Ambujegwe) kalakala (kuti antyochesye). Ni akum’bichilaga Allah milungu kuti ŵasokonesye (najo ŵandu) kuleka litala Lyakwe. Jilani: “Sengwagani ni ukafili wenuo panandipe, chisimu mmwejo n’di mu ŵandu ŵa ku Moto.”"
  39,9,"Ana jwaakulinandiya (kwa Allah ni kuswaliji) nkati mwa chilo pa kusujudu ni kwima ali nkujijogopa Akhera, ni kwembecheya chanasa cha Ambujegwe (mpaka julandane ni jwakunyosya)? Jilani: “Ana mpaka alandane aŵala ŵaakumanyilila ni aŵala ŵangaakumanyilila?” Chisimu ŵaakwete lundape ni ŵaakukumbuchilaga"
  39,10,"Jilani: “E achikapolo Ŵangu aŵala ŵaakulupilile! Mun’jogopani M’mbuje gwenu (Allah). Akwete kupata yambone aŵala ŵaakolosyisye (itendo yao) pa duniya pano, sano chilambo cha Allah chiŵele chakusapanguka (naga nkulepela kutenda ibada upande wine, basi jawulani upande wine). Chisimu akupilila tachipedwa mwakwana malipilo gao mwangaŵalanjila.”"
  39,11,"Jilani: “Chisimu une namulidwe kuti nan’galagatileje Allah mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe.”"
  39,12,“Ni namulidwe soni kuti mbe jwandanda mwa ŵakulipeleka (pakunda Usilamu).”
  39,13,"Jilani: “Chisimu une ngogopa ilagasyo ya Lisiku Lyekulungwa naga naanyosye Ambuje ŵangu (Allah).”"
  39,14,"Jilani: “Allah pe ni jungun’galagatila mwakunswejechesya dini jangu.”"
  39,15,"“Basi jenumanja galagatilagani chilichose chanchisachile changaŵaga Jwalakwe.” Jilani: “Chisimu ŵakwasika ni aŵala ŵatachilijasikasya (Mbepo) achimisyene kwisa soni maŵasa gao lisiku lya Kiyama (ligongo lya itendo yao yangalumbana yaŵaliji nkutenda kuduniya), manyililani yanti kwalakweko ni kwasika kwakuonechela.”"
  39,16,"Takakole ŵanganyao pachanya pao yakusajikanya ya moto, ni pasi pao yakusajikanya (ya moto). (Ni ilagasyo) yalakweyi Allah akwajogoyechesya nayo achikapolo Ŵakwe. “E achikapolo Ŵangu! Basi njogopani.”"
  39,17,"Sano aŵala ŵaaliŵambesye ku shetani kuti akan’galagatila, ni galauchila kwa Allah (pakutenda toba), akwete kupata ŵanganyao abali jakusengwasya (ja kuja kwinjila ku Mbepo), basi mwapani abali jakusengwasya achikapolo Ŵangu"
  39,18,"Aŵala ŵaakupikanilaga maloŵe, ni kugakuyaga gagali gambone nnope. Ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵaŵajongwele Allah, soni ŵanyao ni ŵaakwete lunda"
  39,19,"Ana ajula jwalisimichiche pa jwalakwejo liloŵe lya ilagasyo, ana mmwe mpaka mun’jokole jwali m’Moto"
  39,20,"Nambo aŵala ŵaakun’jogopa M’mbuje gwao (Allah), akwete kupata yumba yapenani yaitaŵidwe mwakusajikanya ine pachanya pa ijakwe, sulo sikajilimeje chapasi pakwe. (Achi ni) chilanga cha Allah, Allah jwangakasa chilanga"
  39,21,"Ana ngankuiona yanti Allah akasatulusyaga mesi (gawula) kuumila kwinani, ni akugajinjisyaga mu achitutumule nkati mwetaka, kaneka ni akasakopochesyaga nago mmela wakulekangana ntundu wakwe, kaneka ni ukasajumulaga ni nkuuwonaga uli wam’bilichila, kaneko ni akasautenda kuŵa wakuteketuka. Chisimu muyalakweyo muŵele mwana chikumbusyo ku ŵaakwete lunda"
  39,22,"Ana mundu jwansapangulile Allah ntima wakwe ku Usilamu, basi jwalakwe ni juli pelanguka lyakuumila kwa M’mbujegwe (mpaka julandane ni kafili)? Ipotesi ili kwa aŵala ŵajijumwile mitima jao pa yakunkumbuchila Allah, ŵanganyao ali mu kusokonechela kwakuonechela"
  39,23,"Allah atulwisye ngani jambone nnope (jajili) Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chakulandana-landana soni chakuwilisya-wilisya. Mapende ga aŵala ŵaakun’jogopaga M’mbuje gwao (Allah) gakasajilijitikaga najo, kaneka ni gakasatependalaga mapende gao ni mitima jao ku yakunkumbuchila Allah, chele ni chongoko cha Allah akasan’jongolaga nacho jwansachile. Sano jwaakunnechelelaga Allah kusokonechela, basi nganakola nkun’jongola"
  39,24,"Ana ajula jwatakaichijeje ni ngope jakwe ilagasyo yakusakala nnope lisiku lya Kiyama (takaŵe nti chisawu jwatakajinjile ku Mbepo)? Ni takasalilidwe ŵalupuso kuti: “Pasyani ayila yamwaliji nkupanganya.”"
  39,25,"Ŵaakaaniile aŵala ŵapaujo pao, basi ni yaichilile ilagasyo kuumila upande wanganaumanyilila"
  39,26,"Basi Allah ŵapele kupasya kwaluka pa umi waduniya, sano ilagasyo ya ku Akhera ni yaikulungwa nnope ingaŵe ŵamanyililaga"
  39,27,Soni chisimu pamasile patupeleche ku ŵandu mu aji Qur’an chilandanyo chilichose kuti ŵanganyao akumbuchile
  39,28,"Qur’an ja Charabu jangali kupombotala, kuti ŵanganyao aligose (ku ilemwa)"
  39,29,"Allah apeleche chilandanyo cha mundu jwajukwete mabwana gakamusyangana gagakangana (mpela mundu jwagalagatila isanamu), ni mundu jwaagamba kuntumichila bwana jumpepe (mpela mundu jwagalagatila Allah pe), ana ŵaŵiliŵa mpaka aŵe yalumo (kaŵe kao) nkwalandanyamo? Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngaakumanyilila"
  39,30,"Chisimu mmwejo ŵakuwa, nombe nao soni chisimu ŵakuwa"
  39,31,Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyammwe lisiku lya Kiyama kwa M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) tinchiŵa nkukangana